arget%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20software%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20CISO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridgewater-tech-chief-igor-tsyganskiy-exits-cybersecurity-microsoft-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIgor%20Tsyganskiy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20responsible%20for%20securing%20Microsoft's%20own%20business%2C%20and%20setting%20cybersecurity%20standards%20across%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20now%20report%20to%20EVP%20Scott%20Guthrie%2C%20who%20runs%20Microsoft's%20Cloud%20%2B%20AI%20group.%20This%20is%20the%20organization%20that%20runs%20important%20business%20like%20Microsoft's%20Azure%20cloud%20and%20the%20teams%20that%20help%20OpenAI%20and%20other%20AI%20companies%20develop%20and%20run%20giant%20AI%20models%20and%20chatbots%20in%20the%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20continue%20to%20navigate%20increasingly%20complex%20global%20threats%2C%20the%20CISO%20team%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20safeguarding%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20Microsoft%20Cloud%2C%20and%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Guthrie%20wrote%20in%20the%20recent%20memo.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20our%20first%20line%20of%20defense%2C%20and%20drive%20our%20services%2C%20products%2C%20platforms%2C%20and%20operations%20to%20be%20secure%20by%20design%20and%20secure%20by%20default.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETsyganskiy%20previously%20reported%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Security%20group%2C%20Charlie%20Bell%2C%20who%20oversees%20all%20of%20Microsoft's%20security%20and%20compliance%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20how%20important%20AI%20is%20becoming%20to%20Microsoft.%20Spokesman%20Frank%20Shaw%20said%20the%20move%20gets%20Tsyganskiy's%20organization%20closer%20to%20the%20systems%20it%20helps%20protect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CISO%20organization%20is%20focused%20on%20protecting%20Microsoft%20and%20our%20customers