re%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESearch%20interest%20is%20up%20for%20retail%20products%20that%20offer%20a%20sense%20of%20security%20in%20uncertain%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20list%20of%20supplies%20suggests%20Americans%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20on%20their%20minds%2C%20from%20war%20to%20weather.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20some%2C%20this%20retail%20therapy%20is%20a%20shortcut%20to%20ease%20concerns%20about%20things%20they%20can't%20control.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20going%20gets%20tough%2C%20Americans%20go%20shopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-us-militarys-strategic-deception-to-strike-iran-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20bombing%20of%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20weekend%2C%20Google%20search%20interest%20for%20topics%20including%20%26quot%3BSurvival%20kit%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BNuclear%20fallout%26quot%3B%20spiked%20in%20the%20US%20to%20levels%20not%20seen%20since%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20late%20February%202022%2C%20data%20through%20Thursday%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Amazon%2C%20data%20from%20marketplace%20analytics%20company%20Jungle%20Scout%20shows%20searches%20and%20sales%20for%20products%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-warning-stockpile-emergency-supplies-experts-say-pack-preparation-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egas%20masks%2C%20first%20aid%20kits%2C%20and%20solar-powered%20flashlights%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20ticked%20up%20notably%20in%20the%20past%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20also%20show%20increased%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3Briot%20gear%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhurricane%20preparedness%20kit%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20same%20period%2C%20which%20suggests%20US%20shoppers%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20on%20their%20minds%20than%20nuclear%20war%20alone.%20The%20product%20with%20the%20largest%20increase%20in%20search%20interest%20in%20the%20Jungle%20Scout%20data%20was%20a%20Uvex%20Bionic%20Face%20Shield%20that%20went%20viral%20earlier%20this%20month%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20anti-ICE%20protests%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20terms%20offer%20a%20lens%20into%20customer%20concerns%20this%20summer%2C%20though%20actual%20demand%20is%20affected%20by%20multiple%20factors%2C%20said%20Jungle%20Scout's%20chief%20operating%20officer%20Tom%20Werle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20prospect%20of%20World%20War%20III%20may%20have%20loomed%20large%20last%20weekend%2C%20it%20seems%20Americans%20might%20also%20be%20anxious%20about%20a%20host%20of%20domestic%20concerns%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20trade%20war%20possibly%20interfering%20with%20essential%20supplies%3B%20civil%20unrest%20surrounding%20arrests%20and%20deportations%3B%20or%20increasingly%20hot%20and%20violent%20wildfires%2C%20tornadoes%2C%20and%20hurricanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20uses%20the%20acronym%20OBE%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bovercome%20by%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20circumstances%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20and%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20a%20mission's%20plan%20and%20preparation.%20Chad%20Huddleston%2C%20an%20anthropology%20professor%20at%20Southern%20Illinois%20University%20Edwardsville%20who%20has%20studied%20prepper%20communities%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20said%20that%20may%20describe%20how%20Americans%20are%20feeling%20about%20recent%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20looking%20in%20their%20immediate%20area%20to%20see%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20that%20to%20determine%2C%20'Well%2C%20what%20should%20I%20be%20worried%20about%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuddleston%20started%20following%20preppers%20back%20in%202008%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20the%20phenomenon%20was%20becoming%20more%20mainstream.%20He%20found%20that%20the%20events%20that%20motivated%20people%20to%20start%20prepping%20then%20weren't%20the%209%2F11%20attacks%20or%20subsequent%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20something%20closer%20to%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20said%20Katrina%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Katrina%20happened%2C%20they%20could%20watch%20on%20TV%20all%20these%20people%20suffering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'Oh%20no%2C%20that%20could%20happen%20here%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20TikTokers%20posting%20about%20a%20possible%20World%20War%20III%20this%20week%2C%20one%20user%20shared%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40fabireyezz23%2Fvideo%2F7519968872175258935%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20how%20to%20build%20a%20survival%20kit%20for%20less%20than%20%2420%20at%20Dollar%20Tree.%20Her%20items%20included%20a%20headlamp%2C%20some%20paracord%2C%20batteries%2C%20a%20can%20of%20beans%2C%20body%20wash%2C%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bit%20of%20retail%20therapy%20in%20the%20form%20of%20off-the-shelf%20solutions%20can%20offer%20people%20the%20illusion%20of%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20and%20people%20that%20I%20probably%20would%20not%20call%20preppers%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20a%20first%20and%20only%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20Huddleston%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20go%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-is-a-doomsday-preppers-paradise-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuy%20the%20Costco%20food%20bucket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20a%20bag%20off%20Amazon%2C%20and%20they%20throw%20it%20in%20the%20closet%2C%20like%2C%20'Cool%2C%20we're%20done.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20true%20preppers%20are%20more%20focused%20on%20skills%20and%20planning%20than%20on%20gear%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20know%2C%20the%20less%20you%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20(who%20can%20afford%20it)%2C%20that%20sense%20of%20comfort%20has%20taken%20the%20form%20of%20investing%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bitter-feud-roiling-doomsday-bunker-business-preppers-shelters-paranoia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafe%20rooms%2C%20underground%20bunkers%2C%20or%20survival%20condos%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0advertised%20as%20able%20to%20withstand%20threats%20ranging%20from%20weather%20to%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20such%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompanies%20told%20BI%20they%20typically%20receive%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funderground-shelter-bunker-demand-rising-russia-ukraine-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20a%20spike%20in%20new%20customer%20interest%20following%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20Iran%20bombing%2C%20but%20calls%20to%20several%20other%20builders%20did%20not%20indicate%20a%20significant%20uptick%20in%20inquiries%20in%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-builds-underground-bunker-survival-prepper-less-than-100k-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efive-%20or%20six-figure%20underground%20shelter%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20likely%20less%20of%20an%20impulse%20buy%20than%20a%20ready-made%20bug-out%20bag%20from%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20more%20immediate%20stuff%20is%20much%20more%20prominent%20in%20people's%20minds%20and%20maybe%20in%20their%20algorithms%2C%26quot%3B%20Huddleston%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f77fdf1-e1fe-4e98-b313-bbd5fe84c92f%5C%22%3EIf%20doomsday%20comes%20to%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20BYOB%3A%20Bring%20Your%20Own%20Bomb%20Shelter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20retail-first%20approach%20to%20disaster%20prep%20also%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20other%20nations'%20civil%20defense%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20countries%20like%20Switzerland%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4c8fepchRwY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinland%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20have%20seen%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einvasions%20and%20ground%20wars%20on%20their%20doorsteps%20in%20the%20past%20100%20years)%2C%20there%20is%20a%20more%20communitarian%20attitude%20toward%20preparedness.%20When%20warning%20signals%20go%20off%2C%20entire%20towns%20can%20seek%20cover%20in%20well-provisioned%2C%20blast-proof%20shelters%20under%20soccer%20fields%20and%20parking%20garages%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerica%20doesn't%20know%20what%20a%20real%20bomb%20shelter%20looks%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Seyfried%2C%20a%20disaster%20preparedness%20consultant%20in%20Utah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeyfried%20has%20designed%20and%20built%20bunkers%20for%20several%20clients%20in%20the%20US%20based%20on%20principles%20from%20nuclear%20science%20and%20European%20practice.%20He%20said%20he's%20skeptical%20of%20the%20efficacy%20of%20many%20of%20the%20more%20heavily%20promoted%20doomsday%20survival%20concepts%20on%20the%20market%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20nations%20that%20invest%20heavily%20in%20hardened%20civil%20defense%20infrastructure%20and%20detailed%20emergency%20planning%2C%20Seyfried%20said%20the%20US%20does%20far%20less%20than%20it%20did%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20main%20messaging%20now%20is%20%26quot%3Bstay%20inside%20and%20listen%20to%20your%20radio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20individuals%20typically%20bear%20responsibility%20for%20building%2C%20supplying%2C%20and%20maintaining%20their%20own%20families'%20disaster%20response%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20also%20generally%20have%20high%20levels%20of%20mistrust%20toward%20the%20government.%20Public%20trust%20in%20the%20federal%20government%20remains%20at%20historic%20lows%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F06%2F24%2Fpublic-trust-in-government-1958-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Pew%20Research.%20A%202024%20FEMA%C2%