acted%20differently%20than%20others%2C%20based%20on%20their%20willingness%20to%20make%20concessions%20and%20work%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20countries%20may%20be%20making%20such%20aggressive%20concessions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fcouncil-of-economic-advisers-chair-tariffs-may-be-here-to-stay-negotiation-deadline-could-extend-153057250.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYahoo!%20Finance%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20convinced%20the%20president%20to%20lower%20tariffs%20below%2010%25.%20There%20are%20other%20countries%20that%20are%20just%20going%20to%20be%20stubborn%20and%20decide%20no.%20And%20then%20they'll%20have%20the%20'Liberation%20Day'%20tariff%20snap%20back%20up%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Miran%20added%20that%20he%20expects%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20extend%20the%20tariff%20deadline%20for%20countries%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bnegotiating%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20making%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20reaching%20the%20type%20of%20resolutions%20the%20president%20is%20seeking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20Trump%20remains%20focused%20on%20using%20tariffs%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20encourage%20US%20companies%20to%20sell%20American%20products%20in%20international%20markets.%20Business%20leaders%20such%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENvidia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20have%20advocated%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-says-us-china-very-close-ai-chip-race-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efewer%20barriers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0to%20selling%20goods%20in%20high-demand%20foreign%20markets%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Miran%20added%20that%20policies%20that%20allow%20more