McConnell%20of%20Kentucky%2C%20the%20former%20Senate%20GOP%20leader%2C%20broadly%20criticized%20DOGE%20efforts%20to%20cut%20wasteful%20foreign%20aid%20spending%20during%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20plenty%20of%20absolute%20nonsense%20masquerading%20as%20American%20aid%20that%20shouldn't%20receive%20another%20bit%20of%20taxpayer%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20McConnell%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20administration's%20attempt%20to%20root%20it%20out%20has%20been%20unnecessarily%20chaotic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20them%20have%20raised%20concerns%20in%20particular%20about%20cuts%20to%20PEPFAR%2C%20a%20global%20program%20to%20combat%20and%20treat%20HIV%2FAIDS%2C%20though%20the%20administration%20has%20insisted%20that%20life-saving%20programs%20will%20continue%20to%20receive%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299bc74cc-a37e-47ce-b841-1fb582faa0c6%5C%22%3E'My%20biggest%20concern%20is%20that%20the%20appropriations%20process%20work'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20senators%20are%20expected%20to%20unanimously%20oppose%20the%20cuts%2C%20just%20as%20their%20counterparts%20did%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Senate%20divided%2053-47%2C%20that%20means%20Republicans%20can%20only%20afford%20to%20lose%20three%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20is%20using%20a%20process%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Brescission%26quot%3B%20to%20pursue%20the%20cuts%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20White%20House%20to%20ask%20Congress%20to%20claw%20back%20money%20it%20has%20already%20approved.%20The%20process%20has%20not%20been%20successfully%20used%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20the%20Senate%20rejected%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-rescission-bill-details-cuts-to-chip-healthcare-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erescission%20request%20in%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20must%20approve%20the%20cuts%20within%2045%20day