mer%20to%20experience%20the%20brand%20and%20car%20in%20a%20seamless%20way%E2%80%94%20being%20able%20to%20start%20the%20car%20with%20the%20app%20alone%20and%20not%20a%20key%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20an%20expectation%20from%20the%20world%20of%20consumer%20electronics%20that%20the%20car%20should%20also%20follow%20that%20same%20seamlessness%20and%20integration%20into%20our%20customers'%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20anything%20that%20we%20can%20do%20to%20enhance%20that%20digital%20experience%20is%20really%20important%20to%20us.%20It%20always%20comes%20back%20to%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20for%20the%20customer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20customers%20of%20e.l.f.%20Beauty%2C%20the%20digital%20experience%20includes%20giving%20feedback%20through%20email%20or%20social%20chats.%20Laurie%20Lam%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20said%20she%20or%20Kory%20Marchisotto%2C%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20reads%20and%20responds%20to%20that%20feedback%20and%20takes%20it%20into%20account%20during%20product%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE.l.f.%20Beauty%20has%20also%20recently%20integrated%20with%20Roblox%20and%20Twitch%2C%20places%20where%20younger%20consumers%20requested%20the%20brand%20to%20be.%20This%20has%20allowed%20the%20company%20to%20connect%20with%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20consumers%20in%20a%20unique%20way%20that%20ultimately%20builds%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELam's%20advice%20for%20exploring%20new%20digital%20platforms%20is%20to%20not%20overthink%20and%20%26quot%3Bjust%20plunge%20into%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20find%20that%20you'll%20learn%20your%20way%20through%20it.%20And%20your%20community%20actually%20doesn't%20care%20if%20you%20don't%20come%20in%20guns%20blazing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20just%20care%20that%20you're%20there%20with%20them%20and%20authentically%20connecting%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BCG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d708cf748d8c055f46ca4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdvertisement%3Cp%3EBCG%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Craddock%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20content%20officer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcmo-alex-craddock-citi-leadership-marketing-content-strategy-cannes-lions-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECiti%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20authenticity%20and%20trust%20are%20important%20for%20any%20brand%2C%20but%20perhaps%20particularly%20so%20in%20the%20financial%20industry.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20as%20consumers%20expect%20to%20be%20able%20to%20trust%20a%20brand%2C%20and%20a%20brand%20has%20to%20keep%20reinforcing%20that%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20Craddock%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20just%20through%20the%20excellence%20of%20its%20product%20and%20customer%20service%2C%20but%20I%20think%20through%20how%20it%20actually%20brings%20its%20products%20and%20its%20services%20to%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20company%20has%20gone%20%26quot%3Bfrom%200%20to%20250%20miles%20an%20hour%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20but%20it%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20because%20it%20feared%20breaking%20the%20trust%20bond%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20company%20is%20pushing%20ahead%20and%20using%20AI%20in%20several%20different%20ways%20across%20its%20marketing%20function%20%E2%80%94%20from%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20summarizing%20reports%20and%20drafting%20emails%20to%20using%20Adobe%20Firefly%20in%20its%20in-house%20agency%20to%20create%20imagery%20and%20build%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMOs%20from%20Salesforce%2C%20Citi%2C%20ELF%20Beauty%2C%20and%20Mercedes-Benz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.co