-Mulekhi-4_11zon-1750856662-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGauri-Mulekhi-4_11zon-1750856662-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGauri-Mulekhi-4_11zon-1750856662-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGauri-Mulekhi-4_11zon-1750856662-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-455888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20fellowship%2C%2059%20fellows%20have%20been%20trained%20to%20work%20in%20animal%20protection%20sectors.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20eight-month%20fellowship%20stands%20out%20by%20training%20individuals%20in%20their%20own%20states%2C%20empowering%20them%20with%20skills%20to%20address%20local%20issues%20while%20collaborating%20with%20a%20national%20network%20of%20mentors%20and%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Sanna%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20committed%20to%20animal%20welfare%20since%202019%2C%20was%20part%20of%202023-24%20cohort.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20Sanna%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fellowship%20begins%20with%20online%20sessions%20followed%20by%20in-depth%2C%20in-person%20workshops%2C%20providing%20participants%20with%20comprehensive%20knowledge%20of%20animal%20welfare%20laws%20and%20strategies%20to%20influence%20policy%20changes.%20I%20learnt%20to%20leverage%20my%20skills%20to%20work%20with%20government%20authorities%2C%20tackling%20large-scale%20issues%20within%20the%20dairy%20and%20pig%20industries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fellowship%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20learning%20theory.%20It%20gives%20fellows%20hands-on%20projects%20and%20real%20assignments%20they%20can%20work%20on%20in%20their%20own%20regions.%20This%20way%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20doing%20more%20than%20just%20theoretical%20learning.%20Instead%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20making%20a%20real%20impact%20from%20the%20start.%20And%20the%20best%20part%3F%20The%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20when%20the%20fellowship%20ends.%20Just%20like%20Sanna%2C%20many%20continue%20pushing%20for%20change%20long%20after%20the%20program%2C%20helping%20improve%20lives%20for%20countless%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20first%20got%20involved%20in%20animal%20welfare%20around%202019%2C%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20longstanding%20passion%20for%20the%20social%20sector.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20calling.%20The%20AIMSA%20Fellowship%20allowed%20me%20to%20take%20this%20passion%20further%20by%20providing%20the%20right%20mentorship%20and%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrior%20to%20this%2C%20my%20efforts%20were%20focused%20on%20rescuing%20individual%20animals%20like%20cats%20and%20dogs.%20However%2C%20the%20fellowship%20has%20empowered%20me%20to%20work%20on%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%2C%20influencing%20policies%20that%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189666%2Fchennai-woman-rescues-animals-shelter-abuse-euthanasia-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20the%20lives%20of%20countless%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20taught%20me%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20and%20leveraging%20laws%2C%20and%20although%20the%20process%20requires%20patience%2C%20the%20potential%20for%20lasting%20impact%20is%20significant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FGauri-Mulekhi-2-1750856598.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gauri%20works%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20animals%20get%20the%20care%20they%20deserve.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https